(43, 7, 33, 43, 13, 33, 33, 'Yet a little while am I with you', 'Jesus'' Temporary Presence', 'Both passages emphasize the temporary nature of Jesus'' presence among his followers. The phrase ''a little while'' in both verses highlights the urgency of his impending departure.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
